column1: makes me question my whole life
screwing with my short term memory
awake in the middle of the night
30-day adderall supply lasts me like a week
If I could lose the 30lbs that I gained from prednisone
I am so sick and angry
light will go out of my eyes soon
eat like the literal beast that you feel
I feel like the devil is living inside my brain, forcing me to think these bazaar thoughts
